The paper discusses a topic modeling technique for authors and documents, which is a common area of research in natural language processing and machine learning. The use of the Hierarchical Dirichlet Process makes it likely that the paper falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) or natural language processing (cs.CL). The focus on topic modeling and document analysis also suggests that the paper could be classified under information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), or data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
